name: 2012-noaa-ortho-rectified-near-infrared-mosaic-of-oregon-columbia-river-bonneville-dam-to-lake
notes: This data set contains ortho-rectified mosaic tiles, created as a product from the NOAA Integrated Ocean and Coastal Mapping (IOCM) initiative. The source imagery was acquired from 20120911 - 20120912. The images were acquired with an Applanix Digital Sensor System (DSS). The original images were acquired at a higher resolution than the final ortho-rectified mosaic.
